c: 3
v: 199
t: "Diggah kitab marak (yahuud kee Nasaara kinnuk) Yalla nummaysaah Qhuraanak siinil obsimtem kee tawraat kee injiilik keenil obsimtem nummaysa mari keenit yanih Yallah aqanxuk, usun Addunya dago duyyê Baxat Yallih Aayoota (Nabii Mucammad weeloolay ken kitoobal tani kinnuk) maxaamitan is elle tani innak tet Koran-korisak, woo mari Qhiyaamah Ayro sinni Rabbih xaqul kaxxa galto-le, diggah Yalli cisab sissikiih isi naqoosak cisab Abam kaa mataanissa"